mulations of the UV theory successfully reproduce the\ncorrect Galileon dynamics at low energies, consistent with the low-pass filter\nmethod and with previous numerical simulations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 11 May 2022 18:00:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 15 May 2022 17:35:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-31"}
