e further evaluate\nthe higher-order efficiency of our proposed estimators by deriving and\nnumerically examining the second-order remainder of the corresponding efficient\ninfluence function in the nonparametric model. Open source software\nimplementing our proposed estimation techniques, the haldensify R package, is\nbriefly discussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 11 May 2022 21:18:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 16 May 2022 18:33:14 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 28 Jun 2022 14:33:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-29"}
