ly used hybrid quantum-classical approach. For pure quantum annealing,\nour method successfully folds an $N=14$ HP chain. The calculations were\nperformed on a D-Wave Advantage quantum annealer.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 12 May 2022 13:30:57 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 12 Oct 2022 10:31:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-13"}
