it. To enlarge success probability amplitude amplification is\nintroduced. We construct a new reflection on stationary state with fewer\nancilla qubits and think it may have independent application.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 12 May 2022 14:08:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-08"}
